== 發展 ==
在1997年初，漫畫書作家凱文·史密斯剛寫完《綠光戰警》腳本，華納兄弟正想著手進行電影工作，但史密斯拒絕提呈，他表示相信還有其他合適的人選來成為《綠光戰警》電影<ref>{{cite news | first = Elston | last = Gunn | url = http://www.aintitcool.com/node/5942 | title = Elston Gunn interviews Kevin Smith | work = [[Ain't_It_Cool_News|Ain't It Cool News]] | date = 2000-05-14 | accessdate = 2011-06-14 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5zx6i3SRm?url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/5942 | archivedate = 2011-07-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。華納兄弟最後想改變成一部喜劇方向的電影，到了2004年，Robert Smigel已完成了以影星[[傑克·布萊克|傑克·布萊克]]為領的腳本。然而，工作室要以喜劇的想法逐漸放棄，因為從網上的粉絲們反應都不佳<ref>{{cite news | first = Larry | last = Carroll | url = http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/11/21/jack-black-green-with-envy-over-new-lantern/ | title = Jack Black Green With Envy Over New Lantern | work = [[MTV|MTV]] | date = 2007-11-21 | accessdate = 2011-06-14 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5zx6iqpI3?url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/11/21/jack-black-green-with-envy-over-new-lantern/ | archivedate = 2011-07-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = Rick | last = Marshall | url = http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/12/15/jack-black-green-lantern/ | title = Jack Black Recalls His Brief Time As 'Green Lantern' Star | work = [[MTV|MTV]] | date = 2010-12-15 | accessdate = 2011-06-14 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5zx6jMzOV?url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/12/15/jack-black-green-lantern/ | archivedate = 2011-07-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。自從看過大衛·S·高耶的《綠光戰警》Flash影片後，華納兄弟公司對他留下了深刻的印象，並提供他了《[[蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻|蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻]]》劇本和導演的機會，但他直接選擇了後者<ref>{{cite news | author = [[Clint_Morris|Clint Morris]] | url = http://www.moviehole.net/news/4718.html | title = Exclusive Interview : David Goyer | work = Moviehole | date = 2004-12-18 | accessdate = 2009-07-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080206124217/http://www.moviehole.net/news/4718.html | archivedate = 2008-02-06 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。經過了演員作家科瑞·雷諾茲漫畫迷和個人角色約翰·史都華的粉絲的想法下，引進了華納兄弟用三部曲的想法，科瑞·雷諾茲主演約翰·史都華和從事編劇工作。雷諾擬引進綠燈軍團哈爾·喬丹可能在《正義聯盟》中的續集<ref name=Melrose>{{cite web|last=Melrose|first=Kevin|title=The Closer co-star wants to pitch Green Lantern film|url=http://blog.newsarama.com/2007/06/18/the-closer-co-star-wants-to-pitch-green-lantern-film/|work=Newsarama|accessdate=2012-07-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523150646/http://blog.newsarama.com/2007/06/18/the-closer-co-star-wants-to-pitch-green-lantern-film/|archivedate=2013-05-23}}</ref><ref name=USAWeekend>{{cite web|title=Corey Reynolds is a superstar on ‘The Closer,’ maybe a superhero as well?|url=http://whosnews.usaweekend.com/2009/05/corey-reynolds-is-a-superstar-on-%E2%80%98the-closer%E2%80%99-maybe-a-superhero-as-well/|work=USA Weekend|accessdate=2012-07-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130208215619/http://whosnews.usaweekend.com/2009/05/corey-reynolds-is-a-superstar-on-‘the-closer’-maybe-a-superhero-as-well/|archivedate=2013-02-08}}</ref>。《綠光戰警》腳本完成了，一個英雄的誕生於2007年6月，由華納兄弟與一個潛在的發布日期-2010年而收到積極的反饋<ref>{{cite news | first = Marlon|last= Bader | title = The ''Closer'' co-star wants to pitch ''Green Lantern'' film | work  = [[Richmond_Times-Dispatch|Richmond Times-Dispatch]] | date = 2007-06-18 | accessdate =2008-02-10}}</ref>。然而，工作室放棄雷諾的想法，並於2007年10月，格雷格勃蘭蒂簽署執導本片，漫畫書作家[[麥可·葛林_(編劇)|麥可·葛林]]和馬克·古根海姆共同譜寫<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117974886?refCatId=13| first=Michael| last=Fleming| title=Berlanti lights up 'Green Lantern': WB set director for DC Comics adaptation| work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]| date=2007-10-28| accessdate=2008-10-29| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zERD953h?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117974886?refCatId=13| archivedate=2011-06-06}}. </ref>。三人的草案於2008年在互聯網上洩露，透露故事和英雄的起源，包括人物托瑪·雷、基洛沃格、塞尼斯托等和一些客串，和海克特·漢蒙的出現將成為哈爾的重大反派<ref>Seijas, Casey. [http://splashpage.mtv.com/2008/08/15/green-lantern-script-a-fanboy-dream-come-true/ "'Green Lantern' Script A Fanboy Dream Come True?"], [[MTV|MTV.com]], 2008-08-15. [http://www.webcitation.org/5zEIwii7p WebCitation archive]</ref>。緊接著，古根·海姆說，該腳本將包含靈感來自丹尼·奧尼爾，尼爾·亞當斯在20世紀70年代的漫畫上運行，和戴夫·吉本斯的作品在20世紀80年代初的刻畫。他補充說，他和他的合作編劇也看了在2000年傑夫·約翰的故事，說「這一直都很有趣，因為我們完成了草案之前約翰就已秘密地將故事線啟動起來，所以我ㄧ直在閱讀這『秘密的OK』，傑夫怎麼解決這個問題有實際利益？有一定的元素，只是為有人試圖於現代觀眾複述哈爾的起源和戰鬥。如，為什麼到底是阿賓在太空飛船飛行時，他的一個綠色提燈？早在白銀時代，你不問這個問題，但在近代卻要你回答這些事」<ref>{{cite news | url = http://splashpage.mtv.com/2008/10/14/marc-guggenheim-drops-the-comics-that-inspire-green-lantern%E2%80%99s-screen-debut/ | first = Kiel | last = Phegley | title = Marc Guggenheim Drops The Comics That Inspire Green Lantern’s Screen Debut | work = [[MTV_News|MTV News]] | date = 2008-10-14 | accessdate = 2008-10-30 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5zEIG0T5K?url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2008/10/14/marc-guggenheim-drops-the-comics-that-inspire-green-lantern%E2%80%99s-screen-debut/ | archivedate = 2011-06-06 }}. .</ref>。

=== 預前製作 ===
2008年12月，編劇寫了三個簡易的劇本稿，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]正準備前期的製作<ref>{{cite news | first = Jennifer | last = Vineyard | title = 'Green Lantern' Co-Writer Marc Guggenheim On Casting Superman’s Cameo And Script Changes | url = http://splashpage.mtv.com/2008/12/01/green-lantern-co-writer-marc-guggenheim-on-casting-supermans-cameo-and-script-changes/ | work = [[MTV_News|MTV News]] | date = 2008-12-01 | accessdate = 2009-02-25 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5zEJUTtr5?url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2008/12/01/green-lantern-co-writer-marc-guggenheim-on-casting-supermans-cameo-and-script-changes/ | archivedate = 2011-06-06 }}. .</ref>。然而，勃蘭蒂被迫遷出華納兄弟導演的位置時，附上了句「這是我離開你的」，並於2009年2月，馬丁·坎貝爾直接進入談判發布日期被定為2010年12月，2011年6月17日之前被推出<ref>{{cite news | first = Michael | last = Fleming | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117999580 | title = Campbell in talks for 'Lantern' | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 2009-02-04 | accessdate = 2009-02-25 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5zEJubefE?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117999580 | archivedate = 2011-06-06 }}. .</ref> <ref>{{cite news|title=''Green Lantern'' and ''Sucker Punch'' Moved to 2011|publisher=SlashFilm.com|date=2009-05-07|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/2009/05/07/green-lantern-and-sucker-punch-moved-to-2011/|accessdate=2009-05-07|archive-date=2009-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090510084521/http://www.slashfilm.com/2009/05/07/green-lantern-and-sucker-punch-moved-to-2011/|dead-url=yes}}. [https://www.webcitation.org/5zEKsskUY?url=http://www.slashfilm.com/green-lantern-and-sucker-punch-moved-to-2011/ WebCitation archive].</ref>。

[[布萊德利·古柏|布萊德利·古柏]]<ref name=collider>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/update-justin-timberlake-ryan-reynolds-or-bradley-cooper-will-star-in-green-lantern/3737/|title=Update: Justin Timberlake, Ryan Reynolds, or Bradley Cooper Will Star in ''Green Lantern''|last=Weintraub|first=Steve|publisher=Collider.com|date=2009-07-09|accessdate=2009-07-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zEL7zeJY?url=http://collider.com/update-justin-timberlake-ryan-reynolds-or-bradley-cooper-will-star-in-green-lantern/3737/|archivedate=2011-06-06}}. .</ref>、[[萊恩·雷諾斯|萊恩·雷諾斯]]、[[賈斯汀·提姆布萊克|賈斯汀·提姆布萊克]]和[[加爾德·勒托|加爾德·勒托]]，這些都是在2009年7月的主演的最佳候選人。在7月10日，華納兄弟公司宣布，由雷諾斯成為綠光戰警哈爾·喬丹<ref name="reynolds">{{cite news|url=http://weblogs.variety.com/bfdealmemo/2009/07/ryan-reynolds-is-the-green-lantern.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100104001536/http://weblogs.variety.com/bfdealmemo/2009/07/ryan-reynolds-is-the-green-lantern.html|archivedate=2010-01-04|title=Ryan Reynolds is the 'Green Lantern'|first=Mike|last=Fleming|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2009-07-10|accessdate=2012-07-15|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

