本片生產所需的預算約為2億美元<ref name="budget">{{cite news | first = Ben | last = Fritz | title = Warner Bros.' 'Green Lantern' marketing campaign delayed by special-effects work | work = Los Angeles Times | date = 2011-03-29 | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/entertainmentnewsbuzz/2011/03/warners-green-lantern-marketing-campaign-delayed-by-effects-work.html | accessdate = 2011-06-15 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5zx6l3KPn?url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/entertainmentnewsbuzz/2011/03/warners-green-lantern-marketing-campaign-delayed-by-effects-work.html | archivedate = 2011-07-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，最初計劃開始拍攝於2009年11月在澳大利亞福克斯工作室<ref>{{cite news | first = Pip | last = Bulbeck | title = Green Lantern to shoot in Sydney | work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date = 2009-04-16 | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i8ff4031e6fcd4bbcc4b63118cb6b7e07 | accessdate = 2009-04-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090419152555/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i8ff4031e6fcd4bbcc4b63118cb6b7e07 | archivedate = 2009-04-19 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。從開始至2010年1月，但生產移至[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]，其中在3月3日，2010測試片段在麥迪遜維爾並以特技車攝製<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nola.com/traffic/index.ssf/2010/03/lake_road_closure_planned_in_madisonville_due_movie_work.html|title=Lake Road closure planned in Madisonville due to movie work|publisher=Nola.com|date=2010-03-02|accessdate=2010-03-15|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zx6mIt9b?url=http://www.nola.com/traffic/index.ssf/2010/03/lake_road_closure_planned_in_madisonville_due_movie_work.html|archivedate=2011-07-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>。主要拍攝始於2010年3月15日在[[新奧爾良|新奧爾良]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://screenrant.com/green-lantern-production-begins-today-rob-48389/|title=Green Lantern Production Begins Today!|first=Rob|last=Keyes|publisher=[[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]]|date=2010-03-04|accessdate=2010-03-15|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zx6mjsRE?url=http://screenrant.com/green-lantern-production-begins-today-rob-48389/|archivedate=2011-07-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>。九天開拍後，安琪拉·芭賽特加入劇組，成為[[DC宇宙|DC宇宙]]中的阿曼達·沃爾博士<ref name="bassett">{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118016867.html?categoryid=13&cs=1&nid=2562|title=Angela Bassett joins 'Green Lantern' cast|first=Dave|last=McNary|work=''[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]''|date=2010-03-24|accessdate=2010-03-25|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zx6neZoB?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118016867.html?categoryid=13|archivedate=2011-07-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>。喬恩·坦尼透露，在2010年4月，他將扮演哈爾的父親，試飛員馬丁·喬丹<ref name="tenney">{{cite web|url=http://superherohype.com/news/greenlanternnews.php?id=9267|title=Exclusive: Jon Tenney is Green Lantern's Dad|first=Scott|last=Huver|publisher=[[Superhero_Hype!|Superhero Hype!]]|date=2010-04-11|accessdate=2010-04-16|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zx6q1Vcg?url=http://superherohype.com/news/greenlanternnews.php?id=9267|archivedate=2011-07-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>。2010年6月已經開始在新奧爾良湖畔機場拍攝<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abc26.com/news/local/wgno-news-green-lantern-behind-the-scenes-lakefront-airport,0,7185051.story|title=Behind the scenes of Green Lantern|publisher=[[WGNO|WGNO]]|date=2010-06-08|accessdate=2011-03-29|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zx6qI121?url=http://www.abc26.com/news/local/wgno-news-green-lantern-behind-the-scenes-lakefront-airport,0,7185051.story|archivedate=2011-07-05|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。同月據報導，麥克·道爾已定的角色傑克·喬丹，為哈爾·喬丹的兄弟。在2010年7月報導稱，瑞安·雷諾茲因受傷而脫離電影拍攝的場景，肩膀有著「很多傷痛」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebritynews/news/ryan-reynolds-injured-on-set-of-green-lantern-2010147|title=Ryan Reynolds Injured on Set of Green Lantern|work=[[US_Magazine|US Magazine]]|date=2010-07-14|accessdate=2010-07-15|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zx6rKFWm?url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebritynews/news/ryan-reynolds-injured-on-set-of-green-lantern-2010147|archivedate=2011-07-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

=== 後期製作 ===
傑夫·約翰已是出了他的[[Twitter|Twitter]]帳戶，電影已經主要結束拍攝於2010年8月6日，並開始進入後期製作階段<ref>{{cite web|url=http://twitter.com/GeoffJohns0/status/20527672185|title=Geoff Johns (2010-08-06).|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2010-07-06|accessdate=2010-08-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zx6rsRSe?url=http://twitter.com/GeoffJohns0/status/20527672185|archivedate=2011-07-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>。導演馬丁·坎貝爾接受MTV新聞採訪時，當被問及電影的效果是重史詩規模，且「這是艱鉅的，只是過程，（有）1300視覺鏡頭一樣的東西，是心靈的吹撲，坦白說」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2009/11/02/green-lantern-director-discusses-intergalactic-and-earthbound-shooting-locations/|title='Green Lantern' Director Discusses Intergalactic And Earthbound Shooting Locations|first=Josh|last=Wigler|publisher=[[MTV_News|MTV News]]|date=2009-11-02|accessdate=2010-03-15|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zx6sReM7?url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2009/11/02/green-lantern-director-discusses-intergalactic-and-earthbound-shooting-locations/|archivedate=2011-07-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>。當要求製造[[能量戒指_(DC漫畫)|能量戒指]]時坎貝爾說「這是漂亮的事情之一，我們都坐下，並說，好吧，我們要在這裡做什麼？真的，這是你的想像力可以盡可能去結構它的」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/02/03/green-lantern-director-describes-the-constructs-created-by-hal-jordan/|title='Green Lantern' Director Describes The 'Constructs' Created By Hal Jordan|first=Rick|last=Marshall|publisher=[[MTV_News|MTV News]]|date=2010-02-03|accessdate=2010-03-15|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zxBq5fFw?url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/02/03/green-lantern-director-describes-the-constructs-created-by-hal-jordan/|archivedate=2011-07-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>。該工作室也證實了MTV新聞，電影將會推出[[三維電影|3D]]版<ref>{{cite web|url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/03/04/green-lantern-will-receive-3-d-release/|title='Green Lantern' Will Receive 3-D Release|publisher=[[MTV_News|MTV News]]|date=2010-03-04|accessdate=2010-03-15|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zxBqMg0S?url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/03/04/green-lantern-will-receive-3-d-release/|archivedate=2011-07-05|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。