== 市場營銷 ==
《綠光戰警》全球首映於[[好萊塢|加州好萊塢]]的[[中國戲院|中國戲院]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://classic.cnbc.com/id/43297278|title=Green Lantern Los Angeles World Premiere Wednesday, June 15, 2011|work=[[CNBC|CNBC]]|date=2011-06-06|accessdate=2011-06-14|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zxBsqAM9?url=http://classic.cnbc.com/id/43297278|archivedate=2011-07-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>，兩天後才在北美和英國發行<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/geoffrey-rush-joins-the-green-lantern-corps-2258897.html |title= Geoffrey Rush joins the Green Lantern Corps |date= 2011-03-31 |accessdate= 2012-08-12 |work= [[The_Independent|The Independent]]}}</ref>。

本片光電影營銷和推廣就耗資了1億美元<ref name="costs">{{cite news | first = Daniel | last = Frankel | title = 'Green Lantern' comes up short at box office | work = [[MSN|MSN]] | date = 2011-06-19 | url = http://movies.msn.com/movies/article.aspx?news=653928&mpc=2 | accessdate = 2011-10-14 | quote = and another $100 million to promote it. | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110625232912/http://movies.msn.com/movies/article.aspx?news=653928&mpc=2 | archive-date = 2011-06-25 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。在2010年[[聖地亞哥國際動漫展|聖地亞哥國際動漫展]]上播出了影片的部分片段。該影片於2010年11月在網上廣為發布。播出第二天就上了《{{link-en|今夜娛樂|Entertainment Tonight}}》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://theflickcast.com/2010/11/15/first-footage-of-green-lantern-hits-the-web/|title=First Footage of 'Green Lantern' Hits the Web|publisher=The Flick Cast|first=Matt|last=Raub|date=2010-11-15|accessdate=2010-11-15|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zxBtjkUN?url=http://theflickcast.com/2010/11/15/first-footage-of-green-lantern-hits-the-web/|archivedate=2011-07-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>。第一個完整的電影預告片在《[[哈利波特－死神的聖物1|哈利波特－死神的聖物1]]》之前放映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worstpreviews.com/headline.php?id=19273&count=0|title=Green Lantern Trailer in November|publisher=WorstPreviews.com|date=2010-10-08|accessdate=2010-10-14|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zxBucdT3?url=http://www.worstpreviews.com/headline.php?id=19273|archivedate=2011-07-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>，於2010年11月在網上面世<ref>{{cite web|url=http://trailers.apple.com/trailers/wb/greenlantern/|title=Green Lantern - Movie Trailers - iTunes|work=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple]]|accessdate=2010-11-17|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5uJB02sXC?url=http://trailers.apple.com/trailers/wb/greenlantern/|archivedate=2010-11-17|deadurl=no}}</ref>。這最初的預告片遭到了粉絲可憐的評價，因此，電影的營銷活動被推遲。Sue Kroll工作室的全球營銷總裁表示：「首款預告片是不冷不熱的反應的部分原因是，大尺度順序還沒有準備好展現，我們遭受了這點，我們不能再這樣做了」<ref>{{cite news|last=Fritz|first=Ben|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/entertainmentnewsbuzz/2011/03/warners-green-lantern-marketing-campaign-delayed-by-effects-work.html|title=Warner Bros.' 'Green Lantern' marketing campaign delayed by special-effects work|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2011-03-29|accessdate=2011-03-30|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zx6l3KPn?url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/entertainmentnewsbuzz/2011/03/warners-green-lantern-marketing-campaign-delayed-by-effects-work.html|archivedate=2011-07-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>。四月華納兄弟公司在[[舊金山|舊金山]]推出九分鐘影片在2011年的{{link-en|WonderCon|WonderCon}}上，《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》報導，這畫面使觀眾叫絕，而遭砍的四分鐘鏡頭則在網上發布<ref>{{cite news|last=Fritz|first=Ben|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/green-lantern-footage-wows-at-174114|title='Green Lantern' Footage Wows at WonderCon|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2011-04-02|accessdate=2011-04-04|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zxBv4P80?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/green-lantern-footage-wows-at-174114|archivedate=2011-07-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

